Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的第18個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對身為重考生的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是不是夏天都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的還是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績一直都沒什麼進步耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼沮喪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個夏天努力用功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就一定能看到成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏天是關鍵時刻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，本須和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳裝你覺得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為了今天而買的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很…很合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ衣服換好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的到海邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是個重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考成績拿 D 的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮又無暇的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，本須和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，週末海邊見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保應該已經跟你說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天兩夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒那個錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺他說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年的這個時候\N都會到海邊的別墅去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們要跟他一起同行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是免費的喔，免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免費…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過我們可是重考生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ泳裝穿這件好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的舊衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐我也邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，那女孩叫裕美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，本須和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克服夏天考驗吧，重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是電腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，跟裕美\N還有清水老師打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是中午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用白天的打招呼法，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還要杵在那裡多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊玩的時間會被耗光的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去幫幫本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多水
