Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
