Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好享受怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呸，好…好鹹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你要東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海水是鹹的，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了\N電腦碰到鹽水不會有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦都有做日常防水\N所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長對電腦也很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢潑我水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起游到那裡去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不勉強你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我可不會讓你溜掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你上特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有間別墅在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家果然真有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是那個對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的私人海灘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒人來這裡玩罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，檢測結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會不會打擾到你們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有點吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的確比較熱鬧呢\N稔少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過偶而這樣也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到了這裡，不需要看書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧！來玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球，秀樹給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的幸福應該就是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不錯的轉換心情方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可沒忘記要用功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經打算今夏要\N從早到晚苦讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著來玩撲克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得清水老師的房間應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我會幫你上特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的課程是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段夏季的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門沒鎖，請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人缺席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拿去抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦用的防腐蝕膏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為海風、鹽水跟沙粒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都算是精密儀器的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是抹一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不是有日常防水了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是幫她保養一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均勻的塗抹在全身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均勻的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我抹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫ちぃ抹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦…辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼辦得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就教她自己塗抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先將防護膏像這樣擠出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生\N要不要我來幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是貝類，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝類，那這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那也是貝類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝類，這也是貝類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會走的貝類？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這個叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是寄居蟹啦，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔對喔，叫寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫寄居蟹喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教她詞句嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ現在還有很多事不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不教她的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昆布嗎？\N不，是裙帶菜嗎？還是海藻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫海草不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草，那是海草，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我也來幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，拜…拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚，是海豚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳的眼力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有海豚耶，海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠們偶而會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，這不是很棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只在電視上看過海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只在水族館看過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，這裡也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遠\N不過真的有看到對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能近一點看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會不會游到這附近來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到近，如果游到這種近海來\N不就回不去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很少有這種機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真想多看一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就游到外面一點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒多遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…學長，難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你說不會游泳\N不是開玩笑的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幹嘛拿這個來開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也會蛙式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任誰都有擅長\N與不擅長的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯考不考游泳這科目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私人遊艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得有點火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會很不公平嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要觀賞海豚\N這一帶是最佳地點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹看到海豚的“嘩啦”\N會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，還不快去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，反正她有日常防水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼深的地方\N日常防水一點用也沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這麼亂來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，不經思索就跳下去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像你的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從表面看來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒進水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思議的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會進水，然後會很難修復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果ちぃ發生事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會變得更麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救本須和起來的可是ちぃ喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夏天結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的還是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是成績進步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績竟然又退步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，夏天熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，夏天真熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個人昏沉沉的，一點精神都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天要用蚊香嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香的味道\N可說是夏天的必需品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天清水老師會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天還是清水老師最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，招待」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.99,0:24:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
